This folder contains the code for producing the result of method “Spatial_1” in the paper.
The full details about this method can be found in the following article.

Grimshaw SD, Blades NJ, Miles MP. Spatial control charts for the mean. Journal of Quality Technology. 2013;45(2):130-148.

Instruction:

1. Run the “simu_baseline.m” to estimate the in-control theta
2.Run “ARL_out_of_control.m” for each shift scenario
